## âœ… 2. Writing Test Scenarios and Test Cases from User Stories
ğŸ“˜ Test Scenario
High-level idea of what to test.

Example:
Test the "Forgot Password" feature for valid and invalid email inputs.

ğŸ“— Test Case (Detailed Steps)
A step-by-step breakdown with expected results.

Step	Description
1	Go to Login page
2	Click "Forgot Password"
3	Enter registered email
4	Click Submit
âœ… Expected:	Success message + Email sent
âŒ Negative Test:	Show error for invalid/unregistered email

ğŸ§  Tip: Always write positive and negative test cases.

